h good and justice through him, with his reappearance You shall expand the servant’s favoured gratefulness. And return the fact to its place with honoured and praised and shall return the Religion and new through his hand, send blessing on Muhammad and on he family of Muhammad.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "وَبِصَاحِبِ الزَّمَانِ الْمَهْدِيِّ، اَلَّذِيْ تَجْمَعُ عَلٰى طَاعَتِهِ الْاٰرَاءَ الْمُتَفَرِّقَةَ، وَتُؤَلِّفُ بِهِ بَيْنَ الْاَهْوَاۗءِ الْمُخْتَلِفَةِ، وَتَسْتَخْلِصُ بِهِ حُقُوْقَ اَوْلِيَاۗئِكَ، وَتَنْتَقِمُ بِهِ مِنْ شَرِّ اَعْدَاۗئِكَ، وَتَمْلَاُ بِهِ الْاَرْضَ عَدْلًا وَاِحْسَانًا، وَتُوَسِّعُ عَلَى الْعِبَادِ بِظُهُوْرِهِ فَضْلًا وَامْتِنَانًا، وَتُعِيْدُ الْحَقَّ اِلٰى مَكَانِهِ عَزِيْزًا حَمِيْدًا، وَتُرْجِعُ الدِّيْنَ عَلٰى يَدَيْهِ غَضًّا جَدِيْدًا۔ اَنْ تُصَلِّيَ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRe