ll, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 2, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Allah’s (s.w.t) choicest blessings be upon Mohammed and his holy progeny.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Parwardigaar Tu rehmat naazil farma Hazrat Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur unki Aal (a.s) par.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! رحمت نازل فرما حضرت محمدؐ اور انکی آل ؑپر۔", "RArabic": "ALLAHUMMA SWALLE ALAA MUHAMMADIW WA AALE MUHAMMADIN", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016762, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Allama Khwajo ei mentions in his Taleeqa that: The line where he says: You will gather the different viewpoints on the point of his obedience; it implicates that in his time of prevailing and mighty governance, the viewpoints and perspectives will not differ from each other and will unify to such an extent that every word and opinion will gather on the path of his obedience. The Imam of Time (a), will be a commander who will be totally accepted by everyone helping each group to attain its right, Khums will be spend on the right place; Zakaat, spoils, charities, fines, Qisas, and all the other rules will be performed righteously and will reach their intended motive.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Allama Khwaja is ebaarat “Al-lazi tajma alaa taa’ate hil-araa-il mutafarreqa” (yaani Aan Hazrat (a)) woh hai jo tamaam mukhtalif nazariyyaat o raaye yek-ja karenge. Yeh abaarat us matlab ko bayaan karti hai keh zahoor keh zamaane mein Aan Hazrat (a) ki kaam-yaab aur pur iftekhaar hukumat ke dauraan mukhtalif aaraa’e aur mukhtalif nafsaani khwaaeshaat na hogi bal-keh sabhi log muttafiq al-qowl aur muttahid ho kar Imam-e-Zamana (a) ke hukm ke mutee honge, woh aise ameer hai keh jin ki sabhi ita’at karenge. Is mubarak aur masood mauqe par har ek ko uska haq milega, khums o zakaat apni jagah musarraf honge aur tamaam ahkaam-e-Ilaahi ka uski jagah par ajra hoga aur mutlaqah hukm ke mutaabiq amal hoga.", "UrduDescription": "علامہ خوجوی نے الذی تجمع علی طاعتة الا راء المتفرقہ اس عبارت کی شرح میں یعنی صاحب الزمان وہ ہے کہ تمام مختلف نظریات اور آراء کو جمع کرکے فرماتے ہیں۔ یہ عبارت اس بات کی نشان دہی کرتی ہے حضرت امام زمانہ کی حکومت کے ظہور میں مختلف آراء نہیں ہونگی بلکہ سب لوگ متفق اور حضرت کی اطاعت میں ہوں گے وہ رئیس ہے کہ سب کے سب اس کی اطاعت کریں گے اس مبارک دن میں تمام لوگوں کو ان کے حقوق ملیں گے خمس اپنے محل میں خرچ ہوگا اسی طرح زکات اور باقی احکام الٰہی اپنے محل میں خرچ ہوں گے اور حقوق کے مطابق عمل ہوگا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016763, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Fadak will be returned to its actual owners and revenge shall be taken from all the enemies of Allah in favor of His friends, irrespective of those who are alive or the dead ones; as they will be resurrected to avenge their enemies. The evidence on the point that we made is the set of narrations which have arrived with relevance to these topics specifically. One of those narrations is the narration which states that soon Allah will return a group of people to this world, at the time of the reappearance of Imam Mahdi (a), who will be a part of those Shias who possessed true faith and have passed away. The purpose of their return will be the attainment of the reward of supporting and aiding Imam Mahdi (a), as well as the happiness they will gain by witnessing the establishment of Imam s government.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Us roz na-haq ghazb ki gayi Fadak, uske maalkin ki taraf palta di jaayegi, aur usi roz Parwardigaar-e-Aalam apne dosto’n ka inteqaam uske dushmano se (jo zindah hai) lega, woh dost chahe ba-hayaat ho ya us daar-e-faani ko wida kahe chuke ho, jaisa keh bohot si riwaayate’n iske mutaliq waarid huwi hai. Min jumla ek riwaayat mein naql huwa hai; Hazrat Imam Mahdi (a) ke qayaam ke waqt Parwardigaar-e-Aalam apne Awliya aur unke Shio’n ke ek giroh ko jo khaalis Imaan rakhte thay, zindah karega, aur duniya mein waapas laaega ta-keh Aan Hazrat (a) ki nusrat ka ajr haasil kare aur Aan Hazrat (a) ki hukumat ke zahoor se shaad o masroor ho.", "UrduDescription": "اس روز فدک کہ جو ناحق غصب ہوا ہے حقداروں کو واپس ہوگا خداوند تعالیٰ اس روز اپنے دوستوں کا انتقام ان کے دشمنوں سے لے گا جو زندہ ہیں چاہے وہ دوست زندہ ہوں یا مردہ ہوں چنانچہ بہت زیادہ روایات اس بارے میں آئی ہیں ان میں سے ایک یہ ہے کہ ایک روایت میں نقل ہوئی ہے کہ حضرت مہدی کے قیام کے زمانے میں کہ خداوند تعالیٰ اپنے دوستداروں اور شیعوں میں سے ایک جماعت جو خالص مومن ہیں ان کو زندہ کرے گا اور ان کو دوبارہ اس دنیا کی طرف واپس لے آئے گا تا کہ حضرت کی مدد کا ثواب ان کو ملے اور اس کی حکومت ظاہر ہونے سے خوش حال ہوجائیں۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016764, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Moreover, the group of people who were absolute infidels will be brought back to the world so that they are avenged, and the part of their punishment and entanglements which they deserved to face, i.e. being killed by the hands of the Shias, will be given to them. Also, they will be humiliated and disgraced by witnessing the powerful governance of his holiness (a). At that noble time, justice, equality and nobility will spread throughout the east and west of the world, just like Allah has defined its occurrence in the holy Quran. Similarly, the divine servants will become mightier and have a fair livelihood, and they will be provided will all that is necessary for them in this material world and for the hereafter. In those days, truth and righteousness will reach its appropriate and valuable position, and the glorious laws of Islam would be re-established and revived after their destruction. In this way, Muslims will accept a fresh Islam and the kingdom of the Earth will totally be in the hands of the divine representatives. How good shall those days be and how good shall be those people!", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Isi tarah kuffaar mahez ke ek giroh ko duniya mein waapas laaega ta-keh un se inteqaam le aur jis azaab ke mustahaq thay uska kuchh hissa chakhe’n, neez zillat o ruswaai ke saath shio’n ke haatho’n qatl ho aur Hazrat (a) ke maqaam o martabe ka hasrat se nazaarah kare’n. Us zamane mein adl o insaaf aur ehsaan Mashriq o Maghrib tal phail jaayega, bilkul usi tarah jaisa keh Parwardigaar-e-Aalam ne Quraan-e-Majeed mein ehsaan o adl ka hukm farmaya hai aur banda-gaan-e-Khuda neymat, rizq aur rozi ki fara-waani mein zindagi basar karenge, us tarah keh unki dunyawi aur ukhrawi (aakherat) dono zindagi kaamil hogi. Is roz sachchaai o haqqaaniyat apni sahih aur ba-azmat jagah pa legi aur us jagah mustaqar ho jaayegi. Deen-e-Islaam jo keh poori tarah na’bood ho chuka hoga phir se raaej hoga, aur log dobaara Islaam qabool kar ke Musalmaan honge. Us roz sirf Khuda ke deen ki poori zameen par hukm-raani hogi pas mubarak ho! Un logo’n ke liye mubarak ho!", "UrduDescription": "اسی طرح ایک کافر جماعت کو بھی اس دنیا میں لے آئے گا تاکہ ان سے انتقام لے اور جو عذاب کے سزاوار ہیں وہ انہیں عذاب ملے یا ذلت کے ساتھ شیعوں کے ہاتھوں سے مارے جائیں اور حضرت کی عظمت کو دیکھیں اس زمانے میں عدل انصاف زمین کے مشرق اور مغرب میں منتشر ہوگا چنانچہ خداوند تعالیٰ نے قرآن مجید میں عدل اور احسان کا حکم فرمایا ہے۔ اور اللہ کے بندے بہت بڑی رزق اور نعمت میں زندگی گزاریں گے ان کی دنیوی اور اخروی زندگی تک ہوگی اس روز سب کے حقوق ادا ہونگے اسلام جو کہ ختم ہوچکا تھا دوبارہ لوٹ آئے گا اور تجدید ہوگی اور لوگ نئے اسلام کو قبول کرکے جدید اسلام لے آئیں گے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016765, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "O Allah, hasten in his appearance, and make the act of his rising easy. And make us one of those who will gather under the shadow of his governance, and will be fortunate enough to witness him; and will fight for him in front of him, killing his enemies and getting killed for him, so that his command attains elevation and his rule becomes powerful, for the sake of Mohammad and his holy Progeny, may Allah bless each one of them.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Parwardigaar! Imam-e-Asr (a) ke zahoor mein taajeel farma aur Hazrat (a) ke zahoor aur qayaam ko aasaan farma, aur Tujhe Muhammad (s) aur Aale Muhammad (a) ka waasta, hamein un logo’n mein qaraar de jo unki ba-karaamat hukumat ke zer-e-saaya zindagi guzaarenge, Aan Hazrat (a) aur unke dosto’n ke deedaar se musharraf honge, aur unke ham-rakaab jehaad karenge, unke kalaam ke ehteraam aur unke deen o millat ki azmat ki khaatir, qatl honge aur qatl karenge.", "UrduDescription": "اے خدایا امام زمانہ کے ظہور میں تعجیل فرما حضرت کے قیام اور خروج کو آسان فرما ہمیں ان کی حکومت کے سایہ میں زندگی گزارنے اور اُن سے ملاقات نصیب فرما۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrd